author: vincent_vda
title: Boris Bulldog (Postman)
review:
A well packed mini set sporting a white-headed bulldog with blue post uniform, yellow pants and lots of accesories.

This set comes with a blue mailbox (can be used w Lego City although a bit big), a carrying basket that can be used for all Fabuland figs and two letters.

One of my favorites as a child...
